[signal arg="hud_hide"]
join bex left
join orion_von_doom right
[signal arg="npc_right"]
orion_von_doom: Greetings, Bex.
[signal arg="player_left"]
bex: Evening, Mayor von Doom.
[signal arg="npc_right"]
orion_von_doom: Please. Call me Orion.
[signal arg="player_left"]
bex: Orion... I've brought your groceries from Lucille. And this package.
join delivery3 (Closed) center
[signal arg="package_delivered"]
[signal arg="npc_right"]
orion_von_doom: Ah, wonderful. Thank you kindly.
leave delivery3
[signal arg="player_left"]
bex: It was no problem at all, really.
[signal arg="npc_right"]
orion_von_doom: You're a phenomenal courier, Bex. Do you know that?
orion_von_doom: It's so difficult to find good couriers these days.
orion_von_doom: Especially ones who do exactly as they're told. You have a commendable sense of duty.
[signal arg="player_left"]
bex: I'm just doing my job, sir. Truly.
[signal arg="npc_right"]
orion_von_doom: You seem nervous. How come?
[signal arg="player_left"]
bex: Ah, well you're the mayor after all. People tend to get nervous around mayors.
[signal arg="npc_right"]
orion_von_doom: Do they? I suppose I wouldn't know. We are quite isolated out here. It gets very... lonely.
orion_von_doom: Have you taken a good look at the lake? It's beautiful, isn't it?
[signal arg="player_left"]
bex: It's sight for sure. The townspeople mention it quite often. Why is that?
[signal arg="npc_right"]
orion_von_doom: You know, Bex... the lake is a living, breathing, entity just like you and I.
orion_von_doom: It requires caretakers. As mere occupants of The Shade, we all must do our part to ensure the town continues to prosper.
orion_von_doom: Do you know why couriers are so important, dear Bex?
[signal arg="player_left"]
bex: Pray tell.
[signal arg="npc_right"]
orion_von_doom: Think about it. Couriers. They connect people. They carry gifts. Necessities. [i]Offerings.[/i]
join delivery3 (Open) center
orion_von_doom: With that being said, let's see what darling Lucille has brought for me today.
update delivery3 (Open) center
