update delivery3 (Knife)
[signal arg="player_left"]
bex: Wh-what the hell?!
bex: I can't do this anymore! I'm leaving! I quit!
[signal arg="npc_right"]
orion_von_doom: Not so fast, Bex.
orion_von_doom: Spend your final moments knowing that you were necessary in keeping the balance of this realm.
orion_von_doom: The lake gives and the lake takes.
orion_von_doom: But most of all...
[signal arg="player_left"]
bex: Wait, wait- No, please, no.
